channel.title: Admin, please come help
channel.description:
I know this probably isn't the right place, but I had a server and was hoping that it would be off the server list after a few days, since I was opening a new one. Here I am 6 days after and it's only down to 72% from 86%, I really need to add my new server, so can an administrator or anybody who can delete it do so?, Thanks in advance, `The One.
The link is: http://www.moparisthebest.com/serverstatus.php?server=godscapepk.servegame.com
